{"tid":1513090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去到依刻無得大家唔認，我地做緊既野係推翻緊一個政權","createTime":"2019-08-28T07:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T09:46:43.000Z","uid":199727,"like":43,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2f5f400787c3a98a3297733e6a014fd7d5caa9fa","tid":1513090,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"仲執著五大訴求最後係徒勞無功<br />\n政府擺明唔接受香港人任何訴求<br />\n我地要贏只可以用任何方式推倒呢個政權<br />\n<br />\n甚至嗌香港獨立都唔過份！<br />\n假設香港有真普選，而有香港人民主授權既行政長官上咗任，都仍然會受到中共干預。因為香港既土地資源及自然資源根據基本法係歸國家擁有，加上外交權喺中共到。<br />\n<br />\n所以應該全民覺醒，我地就算唔嗌出黎，都要心知我地必須推翻政權甚至搞獨立，而唔係成立獨立調查委員會就能平息既問題黎！！！"},{"pid":"604d2e890271cb9d16757a4bda17b168c2d5756e","tid":1513090,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=0597ae1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=6c97fbb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=9b971675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d10f4dc95d90f338957305a022553b79f6d76672","tid":151